neovim bind ideas

ctrl-enter -> open action menu, e.g., like ctrl-enter in opencode
<Leader><Leader> as a "ctrl-shift" kind of overload for less common actions

neovim keys to consider remapping

Z - backspace in normal mode - almost always use something else to delete stuff in normal mode

H & L - top / bottom of screen - rarely useful, prime home row keys

: - will remap to register-replace

m & M - will remap to "move"

